[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1351","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1351.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1137","title":"Sun Solaris 和 SunOS /dev/audio 本地权限许可漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.2 及更早版本、SunOS 4.1.x 系统中 /dev/audio 音频设备的权限配置存在缺陷，允许任意本地用户读取该设备文件。本地攻击者可利用此漏洞监听目标机器附近麦克风捕获的对话内容，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞源于操作系统对音频设备文件访问控制不当，攻击者只需拥有本地账户即可实施监听，无需额外权限。CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1137"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1993-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:47.960","remediation":"升级 Solaris 至 2.3 及以上版本，或 SunOS 至 5.x 系列。如无法升级，手动修改 /dev/audio 权限为 600（仅 root 可读写）：chmod 600 /dev/audio；若无需麦克风功能，可在系统 BIOS 或硬件层面禁用音频输入设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/122&type=0&nav=sec.sba","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/e-01.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/6436","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/549","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/aa3114da1227373bef7855dba21bcaa5f0e0ad76/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1137.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1137","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1137.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4d2ed764072119c12b6f84e6ee4e0df62586a8c4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1137.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-whwh-8wm3-8f72/GHSA-whwh-8wm3-8f72.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88473/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1137.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--63f990c9-7adc-4167-806f-6cfdb2a30758.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--63f990c9-7adc-4167-806f-6cfdb2a30758.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1351.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0298","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0298.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0145","title":"Sendmail WIZ 命令远程权限提升漏洞","description":"Sendmail WIZ 命令漏洞存在于 sendmail 邮件服务器软件中，其 DEBUG 模式的 WIZ 命令默认开启且未经身份认证。远程攻击者可直接连接至 SMTP 端口（25/TCP），发送 WIZ 命令后输入 root 即可获得目标系统最高权限，实现完全控制。该漏洞影响早期版本 sendmail，危害严重，攻击门槛极低，无需任何前置条件即可远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0145"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1993-09-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:41.620","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.6.10 或更新版本（该版本已移除 WIZ 调试命令），或在 sendmail.cf 中注释或移除 `Ow` 相关 WIZ 选项来禁用 WIZ 命令。若无法立即升级，应在防火墙上限制对 TCP 25 端口的访问，仅允许可信来源连接 SMTP 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://seclists.org/fulldisclosure/2019/Jun/16","http://www.alw.nih.gov/Security/Docs/admin-guide-to-cracking.101.html","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1990-11.html","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1993-14.html","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2019/06/05/4","http://www.openwall.com/lists/oss-security/2019/06/06/1","http://www2.dataguard.no/bugtraq/1995_1/0332.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0298.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1352","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1352.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1138","title":"SCO UNIX System V/386 弱默认目录权限导致本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SCO UNIX System V/386 Release 3.2 及其他 SCO 产品（如 Open Desktop、Open Desktop Lite、OpenServer）在安装时错误地将 dos 用户的家目录设置为 /tmp、将 asg 用户的家目录设置为 /usr/tmp。由于 /tmp 与 /usr/tmp 均为允许所有用户写入的世界可写（world-writable）目录，本地其他已登录用户可借此访问这两个账户的目录与文件，进而获取 dos 或 asg 用户的权限，造成权限提升或拒绝服务等安全影响。攻击条件为攻击者需拥有目标系统的本地普通用户账户，并能够向上述世界可写目录写入文件，利用目录权限配置不当即可越权访问相关账户。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1138"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1993-09-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:48.087","remediation":"将 dos 用户主目录由 /tmp 改为 /usr/dos 并设为 700 权限（chmod 700 /usr/dos；chown dos /usr/dos），将 asg 用户主目录由 /usr/tmp 改为 /usr/asg 并设为 700 权限（chmod 700 /usr/asg；chown asg /usr/asg），同时确保 /tmp、/usr/tmp 仅 root 可写（chmod 1777 并去除组/其他写权限）。建议升级至 SCO OpenServer 5.0.5 及以上已修正该配置的安全补丁版本，并审查 /etc/passwd 确认两账户主目录已更正。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1993-13.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/546","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1138.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1138","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1138.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1138.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1138.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/3bc9583077e9d7007badef726c5b3560d73fb205/1999/CVE-1999-1138.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/7d67702de1c8e6c388afcd41c6fc66f9bddaa76f/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-11xx/CVE-1999-1138.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1138.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1138.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1138.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1352.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1404","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1404.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1215","title":"Novell Netware 权限提升漏洞","description":"Novell Netware 4.0 和 4.01 版本中的 LOGIN.EXE 程序在用户登录过程中会将用户名和密码等敏感凭据临时写入磁盘文件，且未妥善保护文件权限。本地攻击者可通过读取这些临时文件获取明文凭据，进而提升权限并接管系统。该漏洞属于本地权限提升类别，CVSS 评分 4.6，影响范围限于 Novell Netware 4.0 和 4.01 版本，攻击条件要求攻击者具备本地系统访问权限。利用方式为直接读取 LOGIN.EXE 生成的临时凭据文件，无需复杂交互即可完成权限提升。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1215"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1993-09-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:57.867","remediation":"升级至 Novell Netware 4.11 或更高版本（已修复该漏洞），或应用 Novell 官方发布的 LOGIN.EXE 补丁程序。若无法立即升级，可限制本地用户对 LOGIN.EXE 临时文件目录的访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/d-21.shtml","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1993-12.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/545","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1f3f1d799c1c9e44bc999093e18341513cabfa3f/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1215.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1215","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1215.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/fb79aaf8eeeb3ec551114292cd7a8693e166aee6/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1215.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6da213119b3c54637329347c0dc42c66b8a84f0a/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cqv7-rg6g-9wmv/GHSA-cqv7-rg6g-9wmv.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88920/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1215.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--8fe008f2-c39d-4acb-8551-ce51d6c8c061.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1404.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0270","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0270.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0124","title":"UMN Gopher 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"UMN Gopher 及 Gopher+ 服务程序（1.12 和 2.0x 版本）存在未授权任意文件读取漏洞。由于 gopherd 守护进程未能对文件访问请求进行充分的权限校验，攻击者可以利用该缺陷绕过访问限制，读取 gopher 守护进程可访问范围内的任意系统文件，包括敏感配置信息。此漏洞无需认证即可远程触发，攻击难度低，对系统机密性构成严重威胁。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0124"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1993-08-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.420","remediation":"升级 UMN gopher 至 2.0.18 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。同时修改 gopherd 配置文件，设置根目录为仅含公开内容的隔离路径（如 /var/gopher），并使用 chroot 机制限制守护进程访问范围。通过文件系统权限确保 gopher 运行用户（如 nobody）对 /etc/passwd 等敏感文件无读取权限。如无需对外提供 Gopher 服务，建议直接停止并卸载 gopherd。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0124"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0270.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1372","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1372.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1162","title":"SCO Unix 4.0 passwd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"SCO UNIX 4.0 及之前版本的 passwd 命令存在安全漏洞，本地攻击者可通过特定操作破坏 passwd 文件或相关认证机制，导致系统无法正常验证用户身份，进而阻止所有用户（包括合法用户）登录系统，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用门槛较低，具有本地访问权限的攻击者即可实施攻击。受影响版本包括 SCO UNIX 4.0 及更早版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1162"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1993-05-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.167","remediation":"SCO 已针对此漏洞发布补丁，建议升级至 SCO UNIX 4.2 或更高版本。对于已停止技术支持的老旧系统，应迁移至受支持的现代操作系统（如 Linux 或 BSD），并确保 passwd 及相关认证组件为最新版本。临时缓解措施可限制不可信用户对系统的本地访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1993-08.html","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/542.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1162.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1162","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1162.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1162.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3gg7-v77p-8v9j/GHSA-3gg7-v77p-8v9j.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88593/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1162.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000036.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c537183d-c5cf-4712-901a-b20fab9ad18b.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1372.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1405","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1405.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1216","title":"Cisco 路由器 IP 源路由安全绕过漏洞","description":"Cisco 路由器 9.17 及更早版本存在安全漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造特定的 IP 源路由数据包绕过设备的安全限制。正常情况下，管理员可通过配置 \"no ip source-route\" 命令来禁止转发源路由数据包，但由于系统对这类数据包的过滤机制存在缺陷，攻击者可利用 IP 源路由选项人为指定数据包传输路径，从而绕过访问控制列表（ACL）等安全控制措施，访问本应受到限制的网络内部资源，导致敏感信息泄露或网络拓扑暴露。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1216"],"sources":["nvd","cve"],"published":"1993-04-22","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"在路由器全局配置模式下执行 \"no ip source-route\" 命令禁用 IP 源路由转发功能，并在受影响接口上应用严格的访问控制列表（ACL）以过滤所有携带源路由选项的数据包。同时应将 Cisco IOS 升级至受影响版本之后的安全版本，以彻底消除该漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T16:54:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/d-15.shtml","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1993-07.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/541"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1405.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1474","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1474.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1312","title":"DEC OpenVMS 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"DEC OpenVMS VAX 5.5-2 至 5.0 及 OpenVMS AXP 1.0 版本中存在未明本地页面管理漏洞，本地攻击者可通过利用系统页面管理机制的缺陷，成功触发后可提升至系统级权限，完全控制受影响系统。该漏洞源于操作系统对内存页面的权限控制不当，攻击者需要拥有本地账户访问权限才能进行利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1312"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1993-02-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:10.310","remediation":"立即升级 OpenVMS VAX 至 V5.5-2 以上版本，OpenVMS AXP 升级至 V1.0 以上版本，并安装 CERT/CC 公告 CA-1993-05 中对应的安全补丁。对于无法升级的遗留系统，应严格限制本地用户登录权限，仅授予可信管理员账户访问，并启用系统审计日志监控异常提权行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1993-05.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7142","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1312.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1312","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1312.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f9199c6ea2112c9d2536a126688b640a45f0982a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1312.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f37077e857e7a28bab83d284c23299407fb1af7e/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w94x-5hjw-v8h6/GHSA-w94x-5hjw-v8h6.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1312.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000034.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--b5b319d3-3501-4f47-b755-2aa6aa228a37.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1474.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0523","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0523.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0312","title":"HP-UX ypbind NIS 数据篡改漏洞","description":"HP-UX 系统中 ypbind（NIS 绑定守护进程）存在安全漏洞，拥有 root 权限的攻击者可通过 ypbind 服务修改 NIS 网络信息服务中的数据。该漏洞影响 NIS 环境下的系统认证与配置信息分发机制，可能导致网络范围内身份认证绕过或系统关键配置被篡改，进而危害整个 NIS 域的安全性。攻击者需先获得本地 root 权限才能利用此漏洞进行数据篡改。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0312"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1993-01-13","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议升级 HP-UX 系统至厂商提供的最新安全补丁版本以修复 ypbind 漏洞，同时严格管控系统 root 权限的授予范围，限制非授权用户对 ypbind 服务的本地访问。对于生产环境，建议评估并逐步迁移至更安全的 LDAP 目录服务替代 NIS 进行身份认证和配置分发。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T13:26:12.646214922+00:00","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0312"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0523.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1310","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1310.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1056","title":"HP OpenVMS Monitor 实用程序本地权限提升漏洞","description":"VMS 操作系统 Monitor 工具（SYS$SHARE:SPISHR.EXE）存在本地权限提升漏洞，影响 VMS 5.0 至 5.4-2 版本。本地用户可利用该工具在处理权限控制时的缺陷，通过执行特制操作获得系统级特权，从而完全控制目标主机。该漏洞 CVSS v2 评分 7.2，危害等级高，攻击者需具备本地访问权限，无需用户交互即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1056"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1992-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:55:06.290","remediation":"此 CVE 编号已被标记为 REJECT（与 CVE-1999-1395 重复），不存在实际安全漏洞，无需进行任何修复操作。请直接参考 CVE-1999-1395 对应的真实漏洞信息进行修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-1056.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/42b5b7a8a9b34b1b292b9bfd27242e499ccb6cb9/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1056.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1056","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1056.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1056.md","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1056.json","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/network-security/index.md","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/61bcf264a889b94a48e2596863419b7c30791e0f/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-10xx/CVE-1999-1056.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1310.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1469","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1469.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1306","title":"Cisco IOS 访问控制列表安全绕过漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 9.1 及更早版本中存在访问控制列表绕过漏洞。当启用 IP 路由缓存且扩展 IP 访问列表中设置了 \"established\" 关键字时，设备无法正确处理已建立连接的过滤规则，导致远程攻击者可通过伪造 TCP 连接状态绕过 ACL 过滤规则，未经授权访问受保护的网络资源。该漏洞影响 Cisco IOS 9.1 及之前版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。Cisco 官方建议升级到不受影响版本或禁用 IP 路由缓存以缓解此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1306"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1992-12-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:09.570","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 9.1 之后的版本（如 9.1.2 或更高），以修复 IP 路由缓存与 established 关键字冲突导致的 ACL 绕过问题。如无法升级，可在接口上执行 `no ip route-cache` 关闭路由缓存作为临时缓解措施，或改用自反访问控制列表（reflexive ACL）替代 established 关键字。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1992-20.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1306.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1306","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1306.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1306.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-363m-9h8j-6gw4/GHSA-363m-9h8j-6gw4.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1306.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000028.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/dd9f81e9fd85457bf78c55783cb6a31e9af71d63/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1469.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0401","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0401.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0214","title":"Sun SunOS 4.1 ICMP Unreachable 报文拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sun Microsystems SunOS 4.1/4.1.1/4.1.2 操作系统存在 ICMP 不可达数据包处理缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标主机发送伪造的 ICMP Unreachable 数据包，导致目标系统内核错误地关闭受影响 TCP 连接，造成合法服务中断。该漏洞影响所有运行上述版本 SunOS 的系统，攻击门槛低、危害较大。厂商已发布相应补丁修复此问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0214"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1992-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:55.663","remediation":"升级 SunOS 至 4.1.3 或更高版本，该版本修复了 ICMP Unreachable 报文处理逻辑。在网络边界防火墙配置规则，过滤外部传入的伪造 ICMP 不可达数据包。如系统仍在使用且无法升级，可考虑迁移至受支持的 Solaris 版本。禁用不必要的 ICMP 响应功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0214"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0401.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0339","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0339.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0168","title":"Sun SunOS RPC Portmapper 代理重定向认证绕过漏洞","description":"Solaris 等 UNIX 系统中运行的 portmapper（端口映射服务）存在访问控制绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的 portmapper 发送特制的服务请求，使其充当代理将请求重定向至本地主机，从而绕过源 IP 认证机制。攻击者利用此漏洞可绕过 NFS 导出限制远程挂载文件系统，获取敏感文件访问权限。该漏洞无需认证即可远程利用，影响面广泛，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0168"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1992-06-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:44.800","remediation":"在防火墙上限制对 TCP/UDP 111 端口的访问，仅允许受信任主机连接 rpcbind 服务。对于 NFS 导出，添加 `-secure` 选项并要求仅从保留端口连接。升级使用支持 RPCSEC_GSS 认证的现代操作系统版本（如 Solaris 10+ 或 Linux 发行版），并启用 iptables/nftables 规则过滤对 rpcbind 的访问。如 NFS 非必要，可通过 `/etc/init.d/nfs` stop 禁用相关服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0168"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0339.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1356","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1356.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1142","title":"Sun SunOS 动态链接程序环境变量注入权限提升漏洞","description":"SunOS 4.1.2 及更早版本中存在权限提升漏洞，本地用户可通过向动态链接的 setuid/setgid 程序（如 login、su、sendmail）设置 LD_* 环境变量（如 LD_PRELOAD）来劫持动态链接库，从而以提升后的权限执行任意代码。该漏洞利用条件为拥有本地系统访问权限，攻击者可通过加载恶意共享库绕过权限检查，获取 root 权限。此漏洞影响范围广泛，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1142"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1992-05-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:48.683","remediation":"升级 SunOS 至 4.1.3 或更高版本，该版本修复了动态链接 setuid/setgid 程序对 LD_* 环境变量的处理。如无法升级，可移除受影响程序的 setuid/setgid 权限位（如 chmod u-s /usr/bin/login），或通过系统安全补丁集禁用 LD_PRELOAD/LD_LIBRARY_PATH 在 setuid 程序中的传递。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/116","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1992-11.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3152","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/aa3114da1227373bef7855dba21bcaa5f0e0ad76/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1142.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1142","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1142.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4d2ed764072119c12b6f84e6ee4e0df62586a8c4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1142.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wx92-67c9-p24w/GHSA-wx92-67c9-p24w.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1142.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5f9a0185-9734-441d-abe3-7193c1e258fc.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/network-security/index.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1356.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1340","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1340.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1119","title":"IBM AIX 匿名FTP配置远程代码执行漏洞","description":"AIX 系统中 FTP 安装脚本 anon.ftp 默认配置不当，将匿名 FTP 服务设置为不安全状态，允许远程攻击者无需认证即可连接目标系统。攻击者可利用该配置缺陷上传恶意文件或执行任意系统命令，导致服务器被完全控制。此漏洞影响 IBM AIX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议立即修复 FTP 服务配置或禁用匿名访问。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1119"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1992-04-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:45.643","remediation":"立即检查 AIX 系统中 /etc/ftpusers 和 anon.ftp 脚本权限，确保匿名 FTP 脚本不可被非授权用户修改。升级 AIX 至已修复此问题的最新维护级别（如 AIX 4.3 及以上版本）。如无需匿名 FTP 服务，建议在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 ftp 行并重启 inetd 以禁用该服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1992-09.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/41","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3154","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1119.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1119","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1119.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1119.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xmf4-5rj8-j896/GHSA-xmf4-5rj8-j896.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1119.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--dc5d0eb4-48b6-40f5-97db-caa33f1b462f.json","https://github.com/augustozarate/integrated-security-scanner/blob/f1af60b35a67d2c1e8d6e4e4cf7bc7b74c32edf0/README.es.md","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/network-security/index.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1340.toml"}]